# Bonehead Labs Site - Project Structure

## Core Architecture
- **Framework**: React 18 with Vite
- **Routing**: React Router DOM (HashRouter)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS with custom CSS variables
- **Animations**: Framer Motion
- **Markdown**: React Markdown with syntax highlighting

## Key Files
- [src/App.jsx](mdc:src/App.jsx) - Main app component with theme state and routing
- [src/main.jsx](mdc:src/main.jsx) - React entry point
- [src/index.css](mdc:src/index.css) - Global styles and CSS variables
- [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js) - Tailwind configuration

## Directory Structure
- `src/pages/` - Page components (Home, About, Projects, etc.)
- `src/components/` - Reusable UI components
- `src/utils/` - Shared utilities and common components
- `src/assets/` - Static assets (images, icons, animations)
- `src/blog/` - Blog utilities and markdown posts

## Theme System
- Uses CSS custom properties for theming
- Light/dark mode with persistent storage
- Theme variables defined in App.jsx: `--paper`, `--ink`, `--cyan`, `--deep`, `--code-bg`
- Theme toggle in navigation header